282
00:11:36,559 --> 00:11:37,640
Bye.

283
00:11:37,840 --> 00:11:38,921
Okay, bye.

284
00:11:39,080 --> 00:11:40,240
- We're good?
- We are so good.

285
00:11:40,480 --> 00:11:41,322
Let's go.

286
00:11:45,879 --> 00:11:46,880
Hmm.

287
00:11:48,039 --> 00:11:49,724
