309
00:12:37,720 --> 00:12:38,960
No, no, no, don't do that.

310
00:12:39,120 --> 00:12:41,326
No, it's--it's...
Hon, I'm fine.

311
00:12:41,480 --> 00:12:43,926
Listen, when you have a birthday
two days before Christmas,

312
00:12:44,080 --> 00:12:45,844
