eating your cake alone.

313
00:12:46,000 --> 00:12:48,206
Mom, you're not eating
your cake alone.

314
00:12:48,879 --> 00:12:51,326
I will, uh...
I'll be right back, all right?

315
00:13:00,679 --> 00:13:01,966
Hey! Can I help you?

316
00:13:02,120 --> 00:13:04,043
Yeah, I'm Gerry Fitzgerald.

317
00:13:04,200 --> 00:13:07,363
I'm an old friend
of Mrs. McGowan's.

318
00:13:07,519 --> 00:13:09,966
Just wanted to stop by,
wish her a happy holiday.

319
00:13:10,120 --> 00:13:11,201
Oh, yeah, yeah.

320
00:13:11,360 --> 00:13:14,091
Um, I'm Nora, I'm one of her nurses.
Come on in.

321
00:13:15,879 --> 00:13:17,484
NORA: Nancy?

322
00:13:18,639 --> 00:13:21,644
Oh, Gerry.
It's so good to see you.

323
00:13:21,799 --> 00:13:23,086
GERRY: Oh, yeah.
[kiss]

324
00:13:23,279 --> 00:13:25,806
Oh, you want a drink?
Nora, get this boy a drink.

325
00:13:25,960 --> 00:13:27,200
Oh, yeah.
What do you want?

326
00:13:27,360 --> 00:13:29,806
