what happened?

404
00:16:32,080 --> 00:16:34,923
The point is that they have no work,
end of story.

405
00:16:37,919 --> 00:16:40,764
Let's go inside, have a beer
and get ready to go to my mom's, huh?

406
00:16:40,919 --> 00:16:42,445
Yeah, I'm not going
to your mom's tonight.

407
00:16:43,080 --> 00:16:45,559
What are you talking about?
It's her birthday, you have to go.

408
00:16:45,720 --> 00:16:46,880
It's bad enough I got to
spend the day

409
00:16:47,039 --> 00:16:48,803
