419
00:18:17,599 --> 00:18:19,364
ABBIE: I can't believe
how big this house is.

420
00:18:19,519 --> 00:18:21,727
- Ah. Well, let me give you the grand tour.
- Oh, thank you.

421
00:18:21,880 --> 00:18:23,244
You ain't seen nothin' yet.

422
00:18:23,400 --> 00:18:24,924
QUINN:
So, what's this guy do for a living?

423
00:18:25,119 --> 00:18:27,167
SHARON: I don't know. Nothing.
It's just, uh, family money.

424
00:18:27,319 --> 00:18:28,605
- Family money?
- Yeah.

425
00:18:28,759 --> 00:18:30,523
