448
00:19:20,960 --> 00:19:23,326
- [Phone rings]
- [Sharon sighs]

449
00:19:25,839 --> 00:19:27,410
[ring]

450
00:19:28,880 --> 00:19:31,166
- Hello?
- CONNIE: Hey, Mom.

451
00:19:31,319 --> 00:19:33,846
