455
00:19:38,759 --> 00:19:40,761
No, no. No, I just, uh...

456
00:19:40,920 --> 00:19:43,287
I bought you a cake and I'm not
gonna be able to bring it over,

457
00:19:43,440 --> 00:19:44,884
so I feel bad.

458
00:19:45,039 --> 00:19:46,929
I don't care about the cake.

459
00:19:47,119 --> 00:19:48,405
