462
00:19:54,440 --> 00:19:57,489
Look, look, baby.
Why don't you come over and--

463
00:19:57,640 --> 00:20:00,769
and stay with me tonight.
Okay?

464
00:20:01,119 --> 00:20:04,727
No, I should stay here.
I'll, uh, I'll talk to you tomorrow, okay?

465
00:20:04,880 --> 00:20:06,369
Have a happy birthday.

466
00:20:06,960 --> 00:20:09,041
- [Phone beeps]
- [sniffles]

467
00:20:14,559 --> 00:20:17,803
Well, looks like
it's just you and me, kid.

468
00:20:17,960 --> 00:20:19,644
So I heard.

469
00:20:19,799 --> 00:20:22,484
Look, Mom, the reason that I wanted
everybody out here tonight--

470
00:20:22,640 --> 00:20:24,881
and for the record,
I am furious with all of them--

471
00:20:25,039 --> 00:20:28,726
