480
00:20:52,000 --> 00:20:53,888
I know, I know.

481
00:20:54,039 --> 00:20:57,964
But in his defense, all right,
he has had a pretty tough year.

482
00:20:58,119 --> 00:20:59,690
Yeah, and I've had a tough life.

483
00:20:59,839 --> 00:21:01,807
