484
00:21:01,960 --> 00:21:03,371
I mean, he lost almost everything.

485
00:21:03,519 --> 00:21:05,840
Good, good. I'm glad.
He deserves it.

486
00:21:06,000 --> 00:21:07,968
Yeah. Well, then you'll love to hear

487
00:21:08,160 --> 00:21:11,800
