1610
01:12:13,159 --> 01:12:15,527
I can't have that man in my house.

1611
01:12:15,960 --> 01:12:17,449
I gotta tell you something.

1612
01:12:18,920 --> 01:12:20,762
My Thomas,
that son of a bitch,

1613
01:12:20,920 --> 01:12:24,002
as much as I hated him
